                                                                                                                                                                                                     Blake in last four
                      
	Houston: American James Blake eased into the semi-finals of the US Clay Court Championship on Friday after a comfortable 6-4, 6-3 win over Argentine Agustin Calleri.         
	Hernandez made the last four for the first time in an ATP event after he upset third seed, and 2006 champion, Mardy Fish 6-2, 7-6.         
	American Wayne Odesnik and Spains Marcel Granollers-Pujol will meet in the other semi-final.         
	Odesnik came from behind for a 2-6, 7-6, 6-1 win over Argentine Sergio Roitman.         
